UPDATE quest_template SET Details = 'This fossil bears a striking resemblance to one I once saw in Ironforge. An archaeologist by the name of Flagongut brought it to our annual Explorers\' League conference. He believed the fossil had a power which could be unlocked somehow.$b$bLast I heard Flagongut had holed up in the Deepwater Tavern in Menethil Harbor, awaiting escort to the Whelgar Excavation Site. Seek him out and show him Remtravel\'s fossil. Perhaps he can reveal the secrets of the past.$b$bThe ship to Menethil departs from Theramore.' WHERE entry = 942;